summary: A sexy Dunmer preset for RaceMenu.
descriptionHtml:
A sexy Dunmer preset for RaceMenu, inspired by one of my favorite presets ever - the beautiful [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/72880]Serine - A Pretty Wood Elf Preset[/url]﻿ by WillingPlatypus, AND descriptions of Barenziah in Biography of/Real Life of Barenziah in game. This is for the face preset only.

[b]Requirements:[/b] 
[url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url]﻿ by ianpatt, behippo, scruggsywuggsy the ferret, and purple lunchbox
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624]RaceMenu[/url]﻿ by expired6978

[b]Recommended (to make sure yours looks just like mine):[/b]
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/7127/?]RANs HeadMesh Variants - Type C[/url] by RAN46
